spec_data.Name: grub2-efi-modules
spec_data.Description:
The GRand Unified Bootloader (GRUB) is a highly configurable and customizable
bootloader with modular architecture.  It support rich varietyof kernel formats,
file systems, computer architectures and hardware devices.  This subpackage
provides support for rebuilding your own grub.efi on EFI systems.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Mon 26 Jun 2017 05:27:40 PM EDT, Key ID 812a6b4b64dab85d
spec_data.Summary: Modules used to build custom grub.efi images
